{"tid":866554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本母女學習斷捨離,丟掉父親的珍藏","createTime":"2018-10-18T03:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T14:09:09.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"423d6a381f909a3b7dd66491d05373a7df6a5da6","tid":866554,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"很多人都會有自己喜歡的收藏，但是當自己結婚以後就會因為各種原因被迫放棄自己的喜好和收藏。有的甚至因為家人的並不理解，從小珍藏的收藏品會被家人不留情的扔掉，也會讓人很是惋惜。最近日本有位經營便當店的爸爸就在電視節目上被自己妻子、女兒的威逼之下丟掉自己熱愛的高達模型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2s0clrf/2p3s000208rn26q92s45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2s0clrf%2F2p3s000208rn26q92s45.jpg&h=4c0b2557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2ik5e8i/2p300001q235o1qqp685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2ik5e8i%2F2p300001q235o1qqp685.jpg&h=9c9a36d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2g89nkh/2p3500020521056q6non.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2g89nkh%2F2p3500020521056q6non.jpg&h=b43f3699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=chep8s/2p37000215909np479s3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dchep8s%2F2p37000215909np479s3.jpg&h=c7a1ac1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本東京電視台近日播出的一檔節目專門幫忙民眾處理不方便丟掉、不知道怎麼丟掉或者捨不得丟掉的物品。鏡頭上一對母女攔下攝影機，表示：「我想請你們幫忙丟掉高達模型」，女兒口中想丟棄的高達模型是爸爸的收藏。這位爸爸從小就喜歡玩高達模型，夢想結婚以後也能夠和兒子一起享受組裝模型的樂趣，然而兒子直到長大都對模型毫無興趣。然後這對母女就表示這些高達模型沒有必要留着，還是趕緊處理掉比較好。<br />\n<br />\n節目將一箱模型搬到店裏質問爸爸：「你說這些該怎麼辦?」女兒和妻子表示：「全部丟掉就好了!」、「只能賣100圓也罷!」、「反正繼續放着也會放到死了，他死了的話就變成普通的垃圾！」。面對這樣過分的話爸爸也開始反擊：「我就抱着它們抱到死！而且為什麼我要被妳們說成這樣啊。」並且表示不想丟掉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=gev52v/2p3700021591rq9828q9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dgev52v%2F2p3700021591rq9828q9.jpg&h=da7d2db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後在攝影機和妻女的威逼之下，爸爸最後還是讓步了，選擇丟掉這些高達模型。"},{"pid":"66bb796c19586a0b2c5209876585ce06bc02ba9e","tid":866554,"uid":35014,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92294512dda13170578ddefd6ae2afb29d296ef0","tid":866554,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6d24314a8795287b324ae26eecb9bb6707987d","tid":866554,"uid":109136,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n點解個兩母女唔掉走自己野先?"},{"pid":"780c7af7711ec9434dc875b9b3a3c98931de3049","tid":866554,"uid":38143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"b087c4450e221c9a11c57ce447d630f51865bfc0","tid":866554,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"就地正法插撚死佢兩母女啦on9"},{"pid":"694dc215b292e73c76783c9cb9a8e566501e5214","tid":866554,"uid":32006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc31720675eb2f09617b63777015bce96f8bf10","tid":866554,"uid":124899,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"又話日本女人好溫柔既"},{"pid":"492ab7e7ed3321fa283e284c9d6d56a929bccabd","tid":866554,"uid":124899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de6d24314a8795287b324ae26eecb9bb6707987d","tid":866554,"uid":109136,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n點解個兩母女唔掉走自己野先?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"女人會自省架咩"},{"pid":"24620fc39ce1e9e44446c5d30a8ed64516b68062","tid":866554,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"搞唔基好過<br />\n啲女人智障架"},{"pid":"45860ef7f325e6fa94590ac9950c8ebe8a502c5b